00:37:13.013 --> 00:37:14.213
pola di dahinya...

00:37:14.653 --> 00:37:15.653
saat aku memberikannya padamu?

00:37:18.733 --> 00:37:19.733
Bentuknya hati.

00:37:20.773 --> 00:37:21.773
Bagus.

